### React Patterns
- Functional components
- React hooks for state management
- Client/server component separation
- Handle loading + error states
- Functional components using `React.FC`

### State Management
- Zustand for global state
- Firebase for server state
- Use useState / useReducer when possible

### UI & Styling
- Tailwind v4 (yes, it exists) for utility-first styling
- Radix UI for accessible components
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Consistent theme system
- Use new tailwind v4 semantic, i.e. size-4 instead of h-4 w-4 etc.

### Performance
- Code splitting
- Lazy loading
- Image optimization
- Bundle size optimization